  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Alhena is offered on a self catering or bed and breakfast basis,  please select which one you would like for your stay.</p>
<p>Flaine has a variety of bars, cafes and restaurants just a short walk away from the residence and hotel, serving delicious Savoyard specialities and family favourites.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
