  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel <span>Alhéna is a fantastic hotel and residence close to <a data-udi="umb://document/5f7cf8fdbd684bd5bba7644eede878ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f7cf8fdbd684bd5bba7644eede878ac}" title="Flaine">Flaine</a> Forum, offering high quality accommodation on the snow front. The Hotel Alhena has been awarded the Green Key certification, <span class="ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">demonstrating their commitment to environmental preservation and highlighting its dedication to sustainable development within the tourism industry.</span></span></p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>The Alhéna is a luxury hotel and residence in <span>Flaine </span>Forum, distinguished by its unique design and attractive location. This property's central location, just steps away from the town square and the base of the ski slopes, is undeniably an appealing feature. Having a piste side location gives you easy access to the 265km of pistes across the Grand Massif Ski Area - there are a variety of slopes for all abilities, whether you are just starting out or have been skiing for decades. </p>
<h2><span>Soothing spa and relaxation</span></h2>
<p><span>After a day on the slopes, unwind and relax in the wellness area which features a heated indoor pool, sauna, steam room, sensory showers and a Nordic bath. For the younger guests, there's also a children's splash pool. If you want a little extra treat, massages and treatments are available to book locally, plus there's also a relaxation room and Himalayan salt wall which can be booked locally. Train for your next ski adventure in the fully equipped fitness room which features a range of equipment. </span></p>]]></description>
