  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 25m² with a view of the slopes. These rooms have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep up to four people and are around 45m². The suites have one double bedroom with an en-suite with a shower or bath open to the room, and a twin room with a shower. These rooms also have a balcony overlooking either the resort or slopes.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms can be made up as a twin or double (please specify at the time of booking)</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobe and slippers</li>
<li>Baby equipment: cots, high chairs, changing mats, strollers and bottle warmers available on request.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
